asset.author: Bed Bath & Beyond

transcripts: Star Wars battle quads are collectible high tech drones. These drones are different because they have reverse propulsion technology which means the propellers are at the bottom of the ship and they are clear so the ships feel like they are actually flying. These drones come with four different settings one is a training mode and there is beginner, intermediate, and advance speed settings. You have the ability to batter other drones. The coolest thing is the package when you open the box and you hear soundtracks that matches ship to the movies. The controller is interactive has ship specific soundtracks. I think beyond the excitement of just seeing the product and experiencing the packaging, the drone itself is one of the best flying experiences you can have out there.
